ResponseRules.description: After following a trail of obscure clues, the player comes into contact with Danielle Sho herself. She's drifting outside of the station. Her suit battery is all but dead and her propulsion system is shot. She only has 15 minutes or so of O2 left, and wants the player to enact vengeance on her behalf for the death of her girlfriend Abby.

ResponseRule.name: Danielle: Morgan at Window, Cook Alive, Needs Sample
ResponseRule.description: The player encounters Danielle while searching for samples of her voice. To cause her to appear the player had to tap on the window with the wrench 3 times which Danielle established with Abby ahead of time. She's drifting outseide the hull speaking to the player via transcribe (or an intercom of some kind), visible outside a window. She's tired, angry, hurt emotionally and physically.

ResponseRule.name: PlayerReturnsToFiona_NotFinished1
ResponseRule.description: The player returns to Fiona, but hasn't dealt with the Cook yet.

ResponseRule.name: PlayerReturnsToFiona_NotFinished2
ResponseRule.description: The player returns to Fiona, but hasn't dealt with the Cook yet. Half of her time remaining has been expended.

ResponseRule.name: PlayerReturnsToFiona_NotFinished3
ResponseRule.description: The player returns to Fiona, but hasn't dealt with the Cook yet.3/4ths of the time remaining has been expended.

ResponseRule.name: PlayerReturnsToFiona_CookEscaped
ResponseRule.description: The player returns to Fiona, but the cook has gotten away. She's angry at first and then morose and resigned to her fate.

ResponseRule.name: PlayerReturnsToDanielle_SheDies
ResponseRule.description: The player returns to Fiona, but she's run out of time. She's upset and moves out of the window to die in private. She does not give the player the passwords.

ResponseRule.name: PlayerReturnsToDanielle_CookDead
ResponseRule.description: The player returns to Fiona having killed the fake Cook. She grants him a passphrase that will get him through the voice lock in Deep Storage, and additionally gives a crucial password or two.

ResponseRule.name: PlayerReturnsToFiona_CookUnconscious
ResponseRule.description: The player returns to Fiona having knocked out the fake Cook.

ResponseRule.name: DanielleMeetsPlayer_Part2LukaIsThere
ResponseRule.description: Danielle sees Luka in the middle of asking the player to kill him.

ResponseRule.name: DanielleMeetsPlayer_Part2LukaIsntThere
ResponseRule.description: Danielle finishes asking the player to kill Luka.

ResponseRule.name: DanielleDoesntWantToSeeTheBody
ResponseRule.description: Danielle doesn't want the player to bring her Luka's body.

ResponseRule.name: Danielle Sees Alien powers
ResponseRule.description: Danielle Sees Morgan use Alien powers

ResponseRule.name: Danielle's Parting Words - Transcribe
ResponseRule.description: Slow building beep in the background if possible, indicating O2 is running out, slowing down as she nears the end
